{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0b86f8ad6b","title":"中共中央关于救济失业工人给中南局的批复","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"343568c33a","index":0,"year":1950,"month":4,"day":20,"articleId":"0b86f8ad6b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"84ae732bd5","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于救济失业工人给中南局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0b86f8ad6b"},{"id":"6fc4838a90","type":"appellation","text":"中南局并告西南局、西北局、华东[南]分局、东北局、华北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0b86f8ad6b"},{"id":"91f97329a3","type":"paragraph","text":"你们四月十六日来电关于救济武汉失业工人的计划收到。中央已经决定在全国各大城市统一地办理失业工人的救济，现正由中央劳动部起草办法中，在中央办法未颁布以前，如果你们有必要可以实行临时救济，而不要宣布长期的失业工人救济计划。现将中央给上海市委的电报发给你们，望你们在必要的情况下参照办理。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0b86f8ad6b"},{"id":"5bfa1d486f","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央四月二十日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0b86f8ad6b"}],"page":{"id":"c9802a70c1","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"0b86f8ad6b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}